Invocation Name: tabata timer
des:
Simple 4 minute Tabata timer for your HIIT (High Intensity Interval Training) workouts. 

Tabata workouts are 8 rounds. 20 seconds of high-intensity exercise followed by 10 seconds of rest, for a total of 4 minutes.
